{
  "stem": "24346.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got my job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I earned money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave me-- I was very willing to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave me plenty of overtime to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And thank God, from that job, I learned to be a butcher, in other words, a hard cutter, that was a place with [? four. ?] I learned to do everything-- trim loins, trim hams, cut the spare ribs.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I learned everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was capable, and I was young, what should I tell you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I learned the helper's pay was, at that time, $1.25 an hour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here, as a butcher, I already got $1.68 an hour.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a lot of money, the difference, here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And besides, the boss liked me, because I was a good worker.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He gave me overtime, and we made a very good living.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then came a time we accumulated a few dollars, and I was offered a business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went into luncheonette business, but I lost my money there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It didn't work out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Went back to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I didn't go anymore to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to a line that was closer to what we had in Europe-- corned beef, pastrami, tongues.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went to such a place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I learned this trade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then came another few years later, another opportunity, a few guys who we knew the trade.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They said, let's go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We can work for somebody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Lets go business for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we went into business for ourselves, five people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We opened up a place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were struggling at the beginning, but it worked out, and knock on wood, we are fine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was in this business till I retired.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
